org.apache.taverna.reference

Interface ReferenceSetAugmentorCallback


  • public interface ReferenceSetAugmentorCallback
    Callback interface used when augmenting a ReferenceSet in an asynchronous fashion through augmentReferenceSetAsynch in ReferenceSetAugmentor.

      • augmentationCompleted

        void augmentationCompleted(Set<ExternalReferenceSPI> newReferences)
        Called when the augmentation has succeeded
        Parameters:
        newReferences - a set of ExternalReferenceSPI instances created during the augmentation process. It is the responsibility of the caller to re-integrate these back into the ReferenceSet used in the translation

      • augmentationFailed

        void augmentationFailed(ReferenceSetAugmentationException cause)
        Called when the augmentation has failed for some reason
        Parameters:
        cause - a ReferenceSetAugmentationException object describing the failure.
